channel.title: InsidiaX 2 Client problem
channel.description:
[b]Hey well i have a problem.
I am using the InsidiaX 2 Source and i have made a webclient with the InsidaX Client too.
1. Me and One other person have tried playing the webclient and the cache has downloaded fine, But 2 other people say they get the 'Error Click for Detail's' Error.. So what's the problem?
2. The Person who COULD download the cache via webclient cannot connect & he gets 'Error logging in'.
I have made sure the IP in the Gui & The client folder are my No-Ip. So i don't see reason whats stopping him from connecting.
You cannot change the IP in the server folder from what i'v seen..
Can anyone help please?[/b]
